    "id": "1956297518859608392",
    "text": "@JackyGekko Eth gained ~25% from ~3700 to 4600, most alts I shorted up 5~15% and I think the profit % of the whole strategy should be like 18-20%. However I closed some ETH long too early cause I thought there will be a pullback, so it actually resulted in a 14% profit for me.",
